<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Interview Preparation Hub</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&family=Roboto:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .info-card {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            padding: 25px;
            width: 300px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .info-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        .info-card h2 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .info-card p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .main-header {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .start-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, green 0%,lawngreen 100%);
            color: black;
            border: none;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-top: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(37, 117, 252, 0.3);
        }

        .start-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(37, 117, 252, 0.4);
        }

        .color-1 { background-color: #e0f7fa; }
        .color-2 { background-color: #f3e5f5; }
        .color-3 { background-color: #fff3e0; }
        .color-4 { background-color: #e8eaf6; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1 class="main-header">Placement Preparation Journey</h1>
    
    <div class="container">
        <div class="info-card color-1">
            <h2>Mindset Matters</h2>
            <p>Cultivate a growth mindset. Every interview is a learning opportunity. Stay confident, prepared, and open to feedback.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="info-card color-2">
            <h2>Continuous Learning</h2>
            <p>Keep updating your skills. Read, practice, and stay curious. The best candidates are those who never stop learning.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="info-card color-3">
            <h2>Preparation Strategies</h2>
            <p>Research the company, practice common questions, and prepare thoughtful questions. Confidence comes from thorough preparation.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="info-card color-4">
            <h2>Self-Reflection</h2>
            <p>Know your strengths and areas for improvement. Be ready to discuss your experiences honestly and positively.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <a href="/option" class="start-button">Start Preparation</a>
</body>
</html>